<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type">
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f7f6; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; }
    .header { background-color: #2c3e50; color: #ffffff; padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; }
    .content { padding: 40px 30px; color: #333; }
    .api-key-box { background-color: #f8f9fa; border: 2px solid #27ae60; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 16px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center; }
    .highlight-box { background-color: #e8f5e9; border-left: 4px solid #27ae60; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #27ae60; color: #ffffff; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; }
    .footer { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #666; }
    .code-example { background-color: #2c3e50; color: #fff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 13px; overflow-x: auto; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üéØ BetStack API</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Welcome, <%= @user.email %>!</h2>
      
      <p>Thank you for signing up for BetStack API. Your API key has been generated and is ready to use.</p>
      
      <div class="api-key-box">
        <strong>Your API Key:</strong><br>
        <%= @api_key %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="api-key-box" style="border-color: #2196F3;">
        <strong>Your Account Password:</strong><br>
        <%= @password %>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Keep these secure!</strong> You'll need your password to access your account at <a href="<%= @account_url %>"><%= @account_url %></a>. You can change your password anytime from your account page.</p>
      
      <div class="highlight-box">
        <strong>‚ö° BetStack Odds, Scores & Sports Data</strong><br>
        Access comprehensive sports data delivered through our global CDN network for lightning-fast performance from anywhere in the world.
      </div>
      
      <h3>Quick Start</h3>
      
      <p>Here's an example request:</p>
      
      <div class="code-example" style="font-family: monospace; white-space: pre-wrap;">curl -H "X-API-Key: YOUR_KEY" [BASE_URL]/api/v1/events</div>
      
      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #666; margin-top: 8px;">
        <strong>Base URL:</strong> api.betstack.dev<br>
        <strong>Your API Key:</strong> Use the key shown above<br>
        <strong>Full documentation:</strong> <a href="https://api.betstack.dev/docs">api.betstack.dev/docs</a>
      </p>
      
      <h3>API Endpoint</h3>
      
      <p><strong>Global Edge Network:</strong><br>
      <%= @edge_url %></p>
      
      <h3>Rate Limits</h3>
      
      <p>Your API key allows requests every <strong>60 seconds</strong>. Perfect for current and up-to-the-minute sports data.</p>
      
      <h3>Available Data</h3>
      
      <ul>
        <li>üèÄ NBA - Current scores & betting odds</li>
        <li>üèà NFL - Current scores & betting odds</li>
        <li>üèí NHL - Current scores & betting odds</li>
        <li>‚öæ MLB - Current scores & betting odds</li>
        <li>üèà NCAAF - Current scores & betting odds</li>
        <li>üèÄ NCAAB - Current scores & betting odds</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p><strong>Updates:</strong> Scores updated every 2 minutes during games, odds updated dynamically.</p>
      
      <p>If you have any questions about the API, reply to this email.</p>
      
      <p>Happy building!<br>
      The BetStack Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>BetStack API | support@betstack.dev</p>
      <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999;">You received this email because you created an account on BetStack API.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

